Woodhaven Boulevard, west side north of Penelope Street, showing the Edxard Tompki s house of 1852. Nicholas Hasselberger owned it in 1873. Other owners were J.J. Tompkins and J.T. Tompkins 1891 and
1896 respectively.
April 1923.
Euocene L. Armbruster Collection
